Package api

Contains classes and interfaces defining the general API of the processing layer.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    API
    The interface as an entry point of the data processing layer.
    CallbackInterface
    The CallbackInterface receives progress updates.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DuplicateException
    An DuplicateException is thrown when, while running the command replace at least two data sets of the same name are encountered.
    NoRepositoryException
    An NoRepositoryException is thrown if a path, which has to point to a repository, does not point to a valid repo.
    UnknownIDException
    The UnknownIDException is thrown whenever a data set identifier does not address a data set.
